<p>This privacy policy describes how Hospital Asset Tracker handles your personal information.</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>We collect the following information:</p>
<ul>
    <li>User account information (name, email, department, job title)</li>
    <li>Asset management data and audit logs</li>
    <li>System usage and activity logs</li>
</ul>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>Your information is used for:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Asset tracking and management</li>
    <li>System security and audit purposes</li>
    <li>Generating reports and analytics</li>
    <li>Communication about asset assignments and maintenance</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information, including:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Encrypted data transmission (HTTPS)</li>
    <li>Role-based access controls</li>
    <li>Comprehensive audit logging</li>
    <li>Regular security updates</li>
</ul>

<h3>Contact Information</h3>
<p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact the IT department.</p>
